Ocamlyices: An Ocaml binding for Yices 1
Mickaël Delahaye

* Requirement

- Yices >= 1.0.26 < 2 <http://yices.csl.sri.com>
  without GMP statically linked
  libyices.so/.a must be installed on the system
  
  you can use './install-yices.sh yices.tar.gz' to install yices in /usr/local
  and register the dll

- gmp.h

- Camlidl

* Install

$ make
to build the library with yices
(the actual linking will be done by ocamlc or ocamlopt when you use the ocamlyices library)
$ make install
install the library in in $(ocamlc -where)/ocamlyices

OR

$ make STATIC=yes
to build the library with yices statically linked
$ make install
install the library in in $(ocamlc -where)/ocamlyices

* Usage

ocamlc -I +ocamlyices ocamlyices.cma ...
ocamlopt -I +ocamlyices ocamlyices.cmxa ...

* WARNING

Hardly tested and only under Linux!

